---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { Container } from '../components/layout/Container';
import { Section } from '../components/layout/Section';
import { Heading } from '../components/ui/Heading';
import { ProcessSection } from '../components/sections/ProcessSection';
import { CTASection } from '../components/sections/CTASection';
import { Badge } from '../components/ui/Badge';

const phases = [
  {
    week: 'Week 1-2',
    title: 'Connect The Dots',
    description: 'Most accounts are broken from day one. You\'re tracking form fills, but Google doesn\'t know which forms became customers. We fix that first.',
    deliverables: [
      'CRM integration: Track actual sales, not just form fills',
      'Waste audit: Identify where 30-50% of budget is bleeding',
      'Tracking fix: Accurate attribution from ad click to sale',
      'Realistic timeline: Clear 90-day roadmap with expectations',
    ],
  },
  {
    week: 'Week 3-6',
    title: 'Build The Foundation',
    description: 'Your old agency launched 20 campaigns with 500 keywords. That fragments data and starves Google\'s AI. We consolidate campaigns and let Google learn.',
    deliverables: [
      'Simplified structure: Consolidated campaigns by customer intent',
      'High-quality keywords: Fewer, better keywords focused on buyers',
      'No daily tweaking: Strategic patience while AI learns',
      'Learning period begins: Google starts identifying your customers',
    ],
  },
  {
    week: 'Week 7-9',
    title: 'Let AI Take Over',
    description: 'Manual bidding is guessing. Smart bidding is Google automatically adjusting prices to hit your goals. But it only works if setup was done right.',
    deliverables: [
      'Smart bidding activation: AI manages pricing automatically',
      'Conversion focus: Optimize for customers, not clicks',
      'Predictable costs: Customer acquisition cost stabilizes',
      'AI pattern recognition: Google finds customers you\'d miss manually',
    ],
  },
  {
    week: 'Week 10-12',
    title: 'Scale What\'s Working',
    description: 'Most agencies try to scale in Week 2 and waste your budget. We wait until the system is trained and the math is predictable.',
    deliverables: [
      'Expansion testing: New customer types Google discovered',
      'Budget scaling: Increase spend without increasing risk',
      'Advanced targeting: Lookalike audiences from real customers',
      'Revenue acceleration: Results compound as AI gets smarter',
    ],
  },
  {
    week: 'Month 4+',
    title: 'Predictable Growth Engine',
    description: 'We\'re not tweaking campaigns daily. We\'re monitoring and maintaining. The AI does the heavy lifting. We guide it strategically.',
    deliverables: [
      'Monthly strategy reviews: Align ads with business priorities',
      'System maintenance: Keep AI trained as business evolves',
      'Expansion opportunities: Test new channels when timing is right',
      'Complete transparency: You see everything, understand everything',
    ],
  },
];

const guarantees = [
  'ROI improvement within 90 days or full refund',
  'Weekly performance reports & optimization updates',
  'Dedicated account manager (not a rotating cast)',
  'Cancel anytime, no long-term contract',
  'Real-time dashboard access 24/7',
  'No hidden fees or surprise charges',
];
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Our 90-Day Profit Sprint Process - ProfitSEM"
  description="See how we turn Google Ads into profit machines in just 90 days. Transparent process, guaranteed results."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <Section background="gradient" spacing="xl">
    <Container>
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center text-white">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur border border-white/20 rounded-full mb-6">
          <span class="text-emerald-400 text-sm font-semibold">
            90-Day Profit Guarantee
          </span>
        </div>

        <Heading as="h1" size="6xl" className="mb-6">
          How We Train Google's AI to Find Your Customers
        </Heading>

        <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 mb-8">
          Most agencies tweak campaigns daily and reset the learning process. We do the opposite: feed Google high-quality data about your actual customers, then let AI do what it does best. Here's exactly how it works.
        </p>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </Section>

  <!-- Main Process -->}
  <ProcessSection />

  <!-- Detailed Phases -->
  <Section background="white" spacing="xl">
    <Container>
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <Heading as="h2" size="4xl" className="mb-6">
          What You Get Each Phase
        </Heading>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          Complete transparency on deliverables
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        {phases.map((phase, index) => (
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-emerald-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl shadow-lg">
                  {index + 1}
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex-1">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                  <Badge variant="info" size="sm">
                    {phase.week}
                  </Badge>
                  <Heading as="h3" size="2xl">
                    {phase.title}
                  </Heading>
                </div>

                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                  {phase.description}
                </p>

                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                  {phase.deliverables.map((item) => (
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
                      <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                      </svg>
                      <span class="text-gray-700">{item}</span>
                    </div>
                  ))}
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </Container>
  </Section>

  <!-- Guarantees -->
  <Section background="gray" spacing="xl">
    <Container size="lg">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <Heading as="h2" size="4xl" className="mb-6">
          Our Guarantees
        </Heading>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          We put our money where our mouth is
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          {guarantees.map((guarantee) => (
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">{guarantee}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200 text-center">
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
            90-Day Money-Back Guarantee
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            If we don't improve your ROI within 90 days, you get a full refund of our management fees.
            No fine print. No questions asked.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </Section>

  <!-- Why 90 Days -->
  <Section background="white" spacing="xl">
    <Container>
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <Heading as="h2" size="4xl" className="mb-6">
          Why 90 Days? (And Why Your Last Agency Failed in 30)
        </Heading>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Google's AI needs time to learn. Your old agency kept resetting the learning process. Here's what actually needs to happen.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-orange-50 border-l-4 border-red-500 rounded-r-lg p-6">
            <p class="font-bold text-red-700 mb-2">‚ùå What Most Agencies Do (Week 1-4)</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Launch campaigns fast, make daily "optimizations" to show they're working hard, panic when results aren't immediate, change strategy in Week 3, reset the learning process, repeat. You're paying them to sabotage your account.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-blue-50 border-l-4 border-emerald-500 rounded-r-lg p-6">
            <p class="font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-2">‚úì What We Do (Week 1-2): Foundation</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              We don't touch campaigns yet. We fix your broken tracking, connect your CRM so Google sees real sales (not form fills), and identify where you're wasting money. Without this, everything else fails.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-blue-50 border-l-4 border-emerald-500 rounded-r-lg p-6">
            <p class="font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-2">‚úì What We Do (Week 3-6): Patience</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              We launch simplified campaigns and then... we wait. This is the hardest month for clients because nothing looks broken, but you're used to agencies changing things daily. We don't. We're letting Google's AI learn who your customers are. Patience here = results later.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-blue-50 border-l-4 border-emerald-500 rounded-r-lg p-6">
            <p class="font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-2">‚úì What We Do (Week 7-9): AI Activation</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Smart bidding turns on. Google starts automatically adjusting prices to hit your goals. Your cost-per-sale becomes predictable. This only works because we built the foundation in Weeks 1-6.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-blue-50 border-l-4 border-emerald-500 rounded-r-lg p-6">
            <p class="font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-2">‚úì What We Do (Week 10-12): Unlock Growth</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Now we scale. The system is trained. The math is predictable. You can confidently increase spend because you know what revenue to expect. This is when clients finally understand why we didn't rush.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-purple-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 rounded-r-lg p-6">
            <p class="font-bold text-blue-700 mb-2">üìà Month 4+: Predictable Growth Engine</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              We're not in emergency mode anymore. We're strategically guiding the AI, monitoring performance, and maintaining the system. You have predictable customer acquisition costs. You can plan your business around it.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 border-2 border-gray-200">
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">
            The Bottom Line
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Other agencies promise results in 30 days because that's what you want to hear. We promise results in 90 days because that's how long it actually takes to train Google's AI properly. If someone tells you they can do it faster, they're either lying or they're going to reset your learning phase every other week.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </Section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <CTASection client:visible />
</BaseLayout>
